file=Engineering/mia/custom/design-tokens/assets/token-schema.md · dts:Design Token Schema — mia/design-tokens — [business name]=> Tokens are semantic names bound to atlas's brand-kit values. Components read tokens only. One token set per theme. Values <FILL_IN> from the kit (rule 0.5 — mia doesn't invent brand values).\n · tb=\| token \| kit source \| value (from kit) \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| color.action.primary \| [kit ref] \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| color.action.secondary \| \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| color.text.default / muted / inverse \| \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| color.surface.default / raised / sunken \| \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| color.status.success / warning / error / info \| \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| token \| kit source \| value \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| type.heading.xl / lg / md / sm \| [kit type scale] \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| type.body.lg / md / sm \| \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| type.font.family (sans/serif/mono) \| \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| token \| value \| · tb=\|---\|---\| · tb=\| space.0 … space.N (scale) \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| radius.sm / md / lg / full \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| shadow.sm / md / lg \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| token \| value \| · tb=\|---\|---\| · tb=\| motion.duration.fast / base / slow \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| motion.easing.standard / entrance / exit \| <FILL_IN> \| · tb=\| theme \| notes \| · tb=\|---\|---\| · tb=\| default \| base token set \| · tb=\| dark \| overrides where they differ \| · tb=\| white-label / per-business \| toongine binds at deployment \| · ru:s=- Components reference tokens ONLY; a raw brand value in a component is a finding.\n- Every token traces to a kit source; a token change traces to the kit amendment.\n- Non-brand one-offs stay OUT of this namespace (local styles).\n